31,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"買左LIKEBOOK<br />\n但其實好多醫書都冇電子版"},{"pid":"4072a79f008e2cca0fac8fa3d192fe49d873c5d4","tid":1783631,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260cd7e5f7f6b644b35dea5736cd96bb310edd82","tid":1783631,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"443c7998a896e2922a3bc7fe5584150ba38b98af","tid":1783631,"uid":45821,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"f3d437df73f738f47c485ec35c8de70bc01e1f03","tid":1783631,"uid":39608,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"電子書聞唔到書香"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"索一索紙味  當堂精神晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"識貨喎ching！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多書有味.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d9e0355a9dd8b9372dfee87741b2200b8197a7","tid":1783631,"uid":323515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"書要一頁一頁咁揭嚟睇先好睇。電子書貪方便望兩下可以，唔會細味內容，唔想細味電子書。"},{"pid":"4a04be449879f1b26b14bfab042b4a12a0586993","tid":1783631,"uid":45265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"327e53b2c4b4dcdbd0dce5e1f1c7adaec7572ff4","tid":1783631,"uid":263910,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"真心電子書係環保好多嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申 環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"紙點都環保過電子儀器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e5490fe7abd99bac0f34f38a7ef3b429e8e23b","tid":1783631,"uid":32442,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74bb3c0e0df2d633d0c9c32fc2e4d073e59bb46","tid":1783631,"uid":21699,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"實體書大幅度揭頁 + 搵野sip住暫時整個書籤 方便好多<br />\n<br />\n我真係好憎 喺鍵盤打個數字去揭頁<br />\n<br />\n你可以話打數字揭頁會快d。但重點係個cognitive load。你需要思考/估邊一頁，開個鍵盤出黎打數字，要click個 entry blank，要等動畫load /忍受個latency.... 真係無人覺得實體書揭頁方便好多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"正常睇書唔駛揭來揭去 除非係工具書 雜誌<br />\n淨係上/下一頁 去返之前bookmark咗嘅地方呢d電子書嘅操作都好intuitive <br />\n有slider快速scroll前後好多頁 唔係必須打數字..<br />\n<br />\n感覺呢個好多留言嘅都唔係好了解近年嘅電子書閱讀器<br />\n例如竟然話電子書比較易爛易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d193c6377ea2e852f85b19f5e9c9fa534a6bffd5","tid":1783631,"uid":201031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"大學啲required readings 大部分都電子<br />\n純粹為知識電子版更方便隨處閱讀翻查<br />\n實體書嘅價值已經唔單止盛傳文字咁簡單"},{"pid":"2b707f33cdc015220d86f0dff336653d02f8465c","tid":1783631,"uid":246670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a070531d9533e9af7fc7d13d6d4bc8d11a7f0902","tid":1783631,"uid":139224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"對於我自己黎講係取代咗<br />\n用咗kindle幾年<br />\n最初動機係覺得遲早冇位<br />\n之後咁我覺得都好方便細細部<br />\n同埋e-book 平好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:58:33.000Z","msg":"Kindle用家 本身貪得意買來玩下 <br />\n用過之後 先發覺比原先想像中好好多<br />\n買書方便 有書想睇就即刻上網買 唔使等<br />\n袋落衫袋又方便 隨時隨地攞出黎睇<br />\n用咗幾個月 睇書嘅時間同機會多咗<br />\n<br />\n不過用電子書翻查資料又的確冇實體書咁方便 揭頁好煩"},{"pid":"40ec94dc67e7e35090f15b582607607a98c3696f","tid":1783631,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"實體書唔使用電"},{"pid":"fa60d6578b05205be4fd247c61cee98a015226d0","tid":1783631,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"已經成日對手機電腦<br />\n唔想睇書都要睇mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋好多想睇的書都無電子版"},{"pid":"5e684fbad616666ba879b76e58b63cd705d008cf","tid":1783631,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"你屋企冇位個時, 乜都取代到."},{"pid":"e8603d2e98378127407b380ef7b824b0a233d324","tid":1783631,"uid":161988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T00:13:58.000Z","msg":"因為一排書排好曬個視覺效果好正 （買書從來齋擺唔睇） 上網睇"},{"pid":"67e91b134caa12e6d2134c868c3717a404802fb3","tid":1783631,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62898c7dd3b0fe4adbfdf76db0fdfabc6b4c605f","tid":1783631,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f0c6ffab27f40389f69fc83272c17f0289acc92","tid":1783631,"uid":22218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"各有各好<br />\n<br />\n實體書有質感有書香<br />\n佢係阻地方，又要有光先睇得，又要特登去買，上網買又要等<br />\n<br />\n電子書夠方便(當係kindle先)同一本書用kindle睇又得電話睇又得電腦cloud又得,睇完一本即刻再買就有，又唔使有光先睇得<br />\n但係繁體選擇真係好少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"Readmoo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"咁就要整多部機<br />\n<br />\nreadmoo有冇app同cloud reader?"}]}